        "market_mechanism": "Alpha Ontology v_alpha_v2 score expansion: v_alpha_v1 11-factor score plus F29 contagion_in_degree (MF-09 co-jump network family, W3.2 strict G6 + G3 passer). F29 is per-subject rolling-60-bar mean of the count of other universe shockers conditioned on self being a 3-sigma shocker; high values indicate systemic-shock exposure. The mechanism is conceptually orthogonal to v91/v_alpha_v1 vol/structure/derivatives signals and the F33 (MF-10) / F12 (MF-04) extensions. Long-short top-3 perp construction inherited from v_alpha_v1_lsk3 (which solved blockers #3 #4 of the v_alpha_v1 strict_validation).",
        "directional_claim": "Same long-short top-3 perp construction as v_alpha_v1_lsk3 (long top-3 + short bottom-3 by 12-factor signed z-score, gross 1.0 / net 0.0). Expected: combined cycle-layer rank IC near v_alpha_v1_lsk3 (+0.180); walk-forward median sharpe stays above v91 baseline (+0.85); regime sign-consistency may improve toward 67% strict (currently 33% under v10) by virtue of F29 broadening the regime-sensitivity profile of the score. Falsified if combined IC drops > 0.005 vs v_alpha_v1_lsk3 OR if F29 weight erodes walk_forward median sharpe below v_alpha_v1_lsk3 (+1.748).",
        "universe_rule": {
          "preset": "liquid_perp_core_20"
        },
